<span class="token punctuation">}</span>
</code></pre><div class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br></div></div><p>至此，路由跳转已经全部分析完毕。核心就是判断需要跳转的路由是否存在于记录中，然后执行各种导航守卫函数，最后完成 URL 的改变和组件的渲染。</p>
